1.title: Ärger im Paradies
1.plot: Warden Dr. Kempers is demoted to warder by the new justice minster, who appoints midget fellow utter bitch Fuchs, to exceed his heartless repressive policy. Manni actually thrives in the new orderly regime, which liberates him of choices or insecurity. Erdem and Alexander find solace in a rundown locked garden, where they dream from escape trough an old near-finished tunnel. Kempers finds out, but decides to oust his successor by proving her incompetence.

3.title: Ein Manni sieht rot
3.plot: While the trio gets re-socializing therapy from psychologist Nora Meindl , the Knackis flirt with her, but Alexander is charming enough to cause jealousy with Erdem, and even drive Manni uncharacteristically furious, while desperately dreaming of matching romantically. Manni goes berserk when his mate, actually just helping out like a gentleman, seems to score kisses.

4.title: Mit links
4.plot: The warden refuses to take notice of the therapist's warning that psychotic new convict Malte, an incorrigible manipulator, will cause great trouble. Indeed he smuggles in sausages as lure, given the vegetarian diet's unpopularity, for a 'left-handed league'. Erdem quickly becomes his gullible lieutenant, to start a conflict with the Russian thugs boss Ivan, but only Alexander sees trough it and makes Manni hold out too.

5.title: Und Action!
5.plot: The therapist gets permission from the warden, who hopes to boast his political ambitions, to let the softy friends Erdem, Manni and Alexander produce a movie in jail. Bu they don't see eye to eye: Manni wants an authentic prison life documentary, Erdem staged action. Involving the Russians -motivated with the promise of privileges- results in unsolicited action, the therapist's clumsiness in uploading the result infuriates the warden.

1.title: Alle mal herschauen!
1.plot: Warden Dr. Kempers intends to fire therapist Nora Meindl as her generally-misbehaving charges seem to systematically insult him grossly. Then Russian mob goon Ivan takes another prisoner hostage by knife, so he dares her to prove she can handle such a violent crisis. It works, and the detainees demand her acceptance of the warden's offer to stay on.

2.title: Hilf dir selbst
2.plot: Fat convict Manni is scared to death, being unable to repay his debt to bully giant Ivan's Russin mob after someone stole his savings from jail labor and the mate'' donations. The jail therapist brings in her personal hero Martin Semmelrogge, who swears by empowerment trough Maori macho warrior attitude, but ignores their real problems. Cellmate Erdem advise improving his physical condition, a hopeless task, but sneaky Alexander discretely thinks up a manipulative ruse.

3.title: Wer bin ich
3.plot: Erdem is shocked when bully guard Schröder shows in his new cellmate, a bossy giant transsexual. A conniving battle ensues of bribery and blackmail, key to which proves Schröder's illiteracy.

4.title: Stresstes Dummies
4.plot: Alexander Vontrab is confident about his chances at the upcoming parole hearing, until the dragon judge arrives, in a lunching mood, and overhears his obscenities about her. rather then trusting their sympathetic prison therapist, whose favorable please in all extant cases discredit her anyway, Alexander's mates hope to boost his confidence, but he's out of cokes, so Erdem, who is frustrated by a kinsman's disloyalty, scores moonshine from the Russian cons, but its effect proves disastrously excessive.

5.title: Vater, Mutter, Knacki
5.plot: Warden Dr. Kempers wants to help his political protector push trough a plan to triple cell population. Therefore he instructs the therapist, who can't refuse anything as she is hired on trial basis, to stage a field experiment proving it would not harm the convicts. She tricks the friends by claiming it's a personal scientific experiment, while the prison has some construction maintenance done, and bribes them with visits and other favors, which the warden didn't back up. The trio starts badly, but son comes to feel their bickering is part of a 'family atmosphere'..*...

6.title: Achtung Freiheit
6.plot: Slick Manni does a better bribery-job then cocky Erdem running for prison population spokesman, but the Russians may support a madman instead. The decisive vote must come from their third buddy Alexander Vontrab, but he's preoccupied with the terrifying prospect of imminent release. Attempts to prolong his term by atypical misbehavior fail, but he can't resist counseling from the foxy therapist, which gets mixed-up with her private claustrophobia experiment.
